---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy — StudyRoadmap™" description="StudyRoadmap™ privacy policy. We collect no personal data. Your exam choices stay on your device.">
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"BreadcrumbList","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Home","item":"https://studyroadmap.in"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"Privacy Policy","item":"https://studyroadmap.in/privacy"}]})}
  </script>
  <Navbar />
  <main id="main-content" class="flex-1">
    <section class="bg-surface-50 dark:bg-surface-950 border-b border-surface-200 dark:border-surface-800">
      <div class="container-page py-14 text-center">
        <h1 class="heading-1 text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-50">Privacy Policy</h1>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="container-page py-14 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="card p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-6 text-sm text-surface-600 dark:text-surface-400 leading-relaxed">
        <p><strong class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100">Effective date:</strong> {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-IN', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
        <p>StudyRoadmap™ is built with privacy as a core principle. We collect <strong class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100">as little data as possible</strong>.</p>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">What We Collect</h2>
          <p>We use <strong class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100">Plausible Analytics</strong>, a privacy-friendly, cookie-free analytics service that collects only anonymous, aggregate page-view data. Plausible does not use cookies, does not track individuals, does not collect personal information, and is fully GDPR-compliant. No IP addresses are stored and no cross-site tracking occurs. We use this data solely to understand which pages are most visited so we can improve our content.</p>
          <p class="mt-2">We do not use tracking pixels, advertising cookies, or any personal data collection. We don't know who you are, what exam you're preparing for, or how long you're studying.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
          <p>We use your browser's <strong class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100">local storage</strong> to save your exam selection and duration preferences. This data stays entirely on your device and is never sent to any server. We use no third-party cookies, no advertising cookies, and no tracking cookies of any kind. You can clear this data at any time from your browser settings.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Your Data Rights</h2>
          <p>Because we collect no personal data, there is no data to access, correct, or delete — it was never here to begin with. If you have concerns about data handled by our hosting providers (Vercel, Cloudflare), please contact us at the addresses below.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>We use <strong class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100">Plausible Analytics</strong> (plausible.io) for privacy-friendly, cookie-free analytics — no personal data is collected or stored. We use <strong class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100">Vercel</strong> for hosting and <strong class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100">Cloudflare</strong> for DNS and SSL. These services may log basic request data (IP, user-agent) as part of their normal operations, governed by their own privacy policies.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Advertising</h2>
          <p>We may display advertisements through third-party advertising networks such as <strong class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100">Google AdSense</strong>. These networks may use cookies and web beacons to serve ads based on your prior visits to our site or other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your visit to our site and/or other sites on the Internet. You may opt out of personalised advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400 hover:underline">Google Ad Settings</a> or <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400 hover:underline">aboutads.info</a>.</p>
          <p class="mt-2">We do not control or have access to any information collected by third-party advertisers. Please review their respective privacy policies for more information.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect any information from anyone under 13. If you believe a child under 13 has provided personal information through our site, please contact us so we can take appropriate action.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this policy occasionally. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Contact</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, reach out to us:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>
              <a href="mailto:contact@studyroadmap.in" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline dark:text-brand-400">
                contact@studyroadmap.in
              </a>
              — for privacy questions and data requests
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/aegisnewsp-rgb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline dark:text-brand-400">
                Open a GitHub Issue
              </a>
              — for bug reports and feature suggestions
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
